---

This addon is independently developed. The Claude Code CLI (installed via
the `@anthropic-ai/claude-code` npm package) is a product of Anthropic and
governed by Anthropic's own terms of service. This addon does not redistribute
Anthropic code; it installs the CLI from npm at build time, like any other
dependency.

Inspired by the Claude Terminal add-on by heytcass
(https://github.com/heytcass/home-assistant-addons), which proved the concept
of running Claude Code inside a Home Assistant add-on. This addon shares no
source code with that project and is written from scratch.
